| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4562 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6f4ba8ef-4bf4-5c98-99f9-4446cd509972"
